test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -7921 == -89
 +  where -7921 = <built-in function prod>([-89, -1, -89])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x76860cf21b00>([-89])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x76860cf21b00> = [[1, -89], [1, -89, 1], [-89, 1], [-89, 1, -89], [1, -89], [1, -89, 1], ...].count
